data.text:
Helper project for converting IBM Rational Rhapsody generated codes to Qt projects. It helps you to convert your Rhapsody codes to Qt with minimum changes.

Second midterm exam project started on Software Specification and modeling course and finished a year later on Software development methodologies course.

An Eclipse plugin that is based on IBM Rational Software Architect (7.5.5.2) and uses medini QVT engine (1.4.0) to transform a source model into a target model with a generated class diagram
